                                The system design will be a community effort, I will be asking local nonprofits to participate in a workgroup to help design the functionality of the system.  I want to hear feedback from the community and build a custom system that meets everyone’s needs.  It doesn’t do anyone any good to build the application in isolation, so I am making the commitment to stay engaged with the nonprofit community and make you a member of the build team.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
