                            <p class="m-2">
                                We are making a commitment to provide weekly progress reports.  Every Friday we will record a screen capture video where we will show the community the progress we made during the week.  We will talk about the features that were added, the obstacles we encountered and our plans for the following week.  We will upload the videos to YouTube and post them here on the website in the “Progress” section.  You will witness the build from start to finish and be able to see how your hard earned money is being put to use.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="d-flex flex-row">
                        <i class="fas fas-question fa-3x m-2"></i>
                        <div class="d-flex flex-column">
                            <h3 class="m-2">Diligence</h3>
                            <p class="m-2">
                                We are committing to give 120% effort to the Community Case Management System build.  Our lives will revolve around building this application as quickly as possible without sacrificing quality.  We estimate that we will have a fully functional beta version within one year of the first line of code.  We also estimate that we will have the analytics and Machine Learning features complete within one year of the application going live.  We are passionate about the mission and will change how social services are delivered in the State of Washington.
                            </p>
                        </div>
